angladesh. UNDP and IDLO gratefully acknowledge the leadership and guidance from the South Asia Association for Regional Co-operation (SAARCLAW) on developing the Regional Legal Reference Resource and co-convening the \u201cSouth Asian Roundtable Dialogue Legal and Policy Barriers to the HIV Response\u201d. The South Asia Regional Legal Reference Resource and accompanying national Legal Reference Briefs for Bangladesh, India, Nepal, Pakistan and Sri Lanka were support by UNDP under the South Asia Multi-country Global Fund Programme (MSA-910-G01-H). TAbLe Of CONTeNTS I. Background 1 II. National Legal Reference Resources 1 III. HIV in South Asia 2 IV. The Role of Law and Policy in the Response to HIV 2 V. Mapping and Resources 3 VI.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "fd537b25-138a-40fe-a484-13187d98b73c": {"__data__": {"id_": "fd537b25-138a-40fe-a484-13187d98b73c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/regional-legal-reference-resource", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Regional Legal Reference Resource", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/regional-legal-reference-resource", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "40e1b6bed3194dbf1968a8d8a40ca47756998de9a41be852614093cf483da394"}, "2": {"node_id": "6c8d2e1d-e420-4822-96a2-7a18d56d473c", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/regional-legal-reference-resource", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "Unit