 reason to believe is likely to spread the infection of any disease that is dangerous to life, shall be punished with imprisonment of either description for a term which may extend to six (6) months or with fine or with both. 5 2 Section 270 \u2013 Malignant Act likely to spread infection of disease dangerous to life 5.2.1 Section 270 of the PPC pertains to the offence where a person", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "9582a924-52dc-4d33-a58e-77b18c656016": {"__data__": {"id_": "9582a924-52dc-4d33-a58e-77b18c656016", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/scan-law-and-policies-affecting-human-rights-discrimination-and-access-hiv-and-health-services-key-populations-pakistan", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Scan of Law and Policies Affecting Human Rights, Discrimination and Access to HIV and Health Services by Key Populations in Pakistan", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/scan-law-and-policies-affecting-human-rights-discrimination-and-access-hiv-and-health-services-key-populations-pakistan", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "51492ba01250da06eedd5bc1282fc9ce2bb29de6c92e2900a38b28beee102ae8"}, "3": {"node_id": "e8920d50-127c-4abe-ad0b-5ff7fc6643a4", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/scan-law-and-policies-affecting-human-rights-discrimination-and-access-hiv-and-health-services-key-populations-pakistan", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "Un